{{!-- Demo/evaluation help box. Renders page-specific guidance based on the `page` variable. --}}
{{#if (eq page "control-center")}}
<div class="demo-help-box">
    <div class="demo-help-box__header">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
        <strong>Demo Environment</strong>
    </div>
    <p>The <strong>Control Center</strong> is your real-time operations hub. It shows live Claude sessions, APM (Actions Per Minute) metrics, conversation history, skill effectiveness ratings, and session health analytics. In a production deployment, this page streams live updates via SSE as your team uses Claude, giving you instant visibility into AI usage patterns and performance.</p>
    <p class="demo-help-box__footer">This dashboard has been configured for demo and evaluation purposes. Some features may not be fully functional. For a deeper look at any feature, contact <a href="mailto:ed@systemprompt.io">ed@systemprompt.io</a></p>
</div>
{{else if (eq page "profile")}}
<div class="demo-help-box">
    <div class="demo-help-box__header">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
        <strong>Demo Environment</strong>
    </div>
    <p><strong>Profile &amp; Insights</strong> analyses your usage patterns to identify your user archetype, strengths, and areas for improvement. It aggregates 30 days of Claude session data into behavioral analytics, comparing your usage against global averages. This helps teams understand how individuals interact with AI and where additional training or skills could help.</p>
    <p class="demo-help-box__footer">This dashboard has been configured for demo and evaluation purposes. Some features may not be fully functional. For a deeper look at any feature, contact <a href="mailto:ed@systemprompt.io">ed@systemprompt.io</a></p>
</div>
