    <p><strong>My Plugins</strong> shows all plugins installed in your workspace. Plugins are the core building block &mdash; each bundles skills (prompt templates), agents (specialized Claude configurations), and MCP server connections. You can customize any plugin's components, fork official plugins, or create your own. Enterprise deployments can control which plugins are available to users.</p>
    <p class="demo-help-box__footer">This dashboard has been configured for demo and evaluation purposes. Some features may not be fully functional. For a deeper look at any feature, contact <a href="mailto:ed@systemprompt.io">ed@systemprompt.io</a></p>
