    <p>The <strong>Plugin Directory</strong> is where you discover and install plugins from the marketplace. Each plugin is a curated bundle of skills, agents, and integrations that extends Claude's capabilities. Once installed, plugins appear in My Plugins where you can customize them for your workflow.</p>
