    <p><strong>My Skills</strong> manages the prompt templates and instructions that guide Claude's behavior. Skills are the most granular customization unit &mdash; each defines how Claude should handle a specific type of task. Skills can be shared across plugins and are tracked for usage and effectiveness.</p>
