        <strong>Demo Environment</strong>
    </div>
    <p><strong>My MCP Servers</strong> displays the Model Context Protocol server connections in your workspace. These MCP servers run on this host and extend Claude's capabilities by providing external tools and data sources. Each server exposes API endpoints that Claude can call during conversations. Authentication is handled via API keys configured in My Secrets.</p>
    <p class="demo-help-box__footer">This dashboard has been configured for demo and evaluation purposes. Some features may not be fully functional. For a deeper look at any feature, contact <a href="mailto:ed@systemprompt.io">ed@systemprompt.io</a></p>
