        <strong>Demo Environment</strong>
    </div>
    <p><strong>My Secrets</strong> manages API keys and environment variables used by your plugins and MCP servers. Secrets are encrypted at rest and scoped per plugin, ensuring that each integration only accesses its own credentials. This is where you configure authentication for external services.</p>
    <p class="demo-help-box__footer">This dashboard has been configured for demo and evaluation purposes. Some features may not be fully functional. For a deeper look at any feature, contact <a href="mailto:ed@systemprompt.io">ed@systemprompt.io</a></p>
