    <p><strong>My Hooks</strong> manages event handlers that fire during Claude Code sessions. Hooks intercept events like PreToolUse, PostToolUse, SessionStart, and PermissionRequest, enabling custom behavior at each stage. In production, hooks power analytics tracking, compliance logging, and automated workflows.</p>
    <p class="demo-help-box__footer">This dashboard has been configured for demo and evaluation purposes. Some features may not be fully functional. For a deeper look at any feature, contact <a href="mailto:ed@systemprompt.io">ed@systemprompt.io</a></p>
